OL,3,CTrump weighs up Kharg Island invasion
OL,4,Cas Israel launches fresh attack on Iran
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump has said he
OL,7,Fis considering a ground invasion of
OL,8,Fmajor Iranian fuel hub Kharg Island,
OL,9,Fwarning he could "take the oil in
OL,10,FIran."
OL,12,FHis words came as Israel launched a
OL,13,Fnew offensive on Tehran during the
OL,14,Fearly hours on Monday morning.
OL,16,FSpeaking in an interview with the
OL,17,FFinancial Times, Trump said his
OL,18,F"favourite thing" is to "take the oil
OL,19,Fin Iran."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774947927
OL,3,CTrump weighs up Kharg Island invasion
OL,4,Cas Israel launches fresh attack on Iran
OL,6,F"Maybe we take Kharg Island, maybe we
OL,7,Fdon't. We have a lot of options," he
OL,8,Fsaid, referring to the island where
OL,9,Fmost of Iran's oil is exported. "It
OL,10,Fwould also mean we had to be there for
OL,11,Fa while."
OL,13,FThousands of US troops began arriving
OL,14,Fin Iran as the conflict entered its
OL,15,Ffifth week, despite Trump stating that
OL,16,Fboth countries are attempting to
OL,17,Fnegotiate a ceasefire in recent days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
