FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774947927
OL,3,CTrump weighs up Kharg Island invasion
OL,4,Cas Israel launches fresh attack on Iran
OL,6,FHis comments also came as Brent crude
OL,7,Foil - used as the global benchmark for
OL,8,Fprices - topped $116 (#87.37) a barrel
OL,9,Fduring trading early on Monday.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FEarlier, Iran's parliament speaker
OL,17,FMohammad Bagher Qalibaf said the
OL,18,Fcountry's forces are "waiting for the
OL,19,Farrival of American troops on the
OL,20,Fground to set them on fire".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
