PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774947927
OL,3,CTrump weighs up Kharg Island invasion
OL,4,Cas Israel launches fresh attack on Iran
OL,6,FQalibaf added: "Our firing continues.
OL,7,FOur missiles are in place. Our
OL,8,Fdetermination and faith have
OL,9,Fincreased."
OL,11,FMeanwhile, Israel's military upped
OL,12,Fattacks on infrastructure across
OL,13,FTehran on Monday morning, while
OL,14,FIranian strikes on a power and
OL,15,Fdesalination plant killed a worker in
OL,16,FKuwait.
OL,18,FA UN peacekeeper was killed and
OL,19,Fanother injured by a projectile in
OL,20,Fsouthern Lebanon, the UN Interim Force
OL,21,Fin Lebanon said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
