PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774947927
OL,3,CTrump weighs up Kharg Island invasion
OL,4,Cas Israel launches fresh attack on Iran
OL,6,FTrump wants to "take the oil in Iran"
OL,8,FThe US president has refused to rule
OL,9,Fout a land invasion on Kharg Island,
OL,10,FIran's primary oil hub, where more
OL,11,Fthan 94% of its exports originate.
OL,13,FAround 2,500 US Marines arrived in the
OL,14,Fregion last week, while thousands more
OL,15,Fare on their way, as well troops from
OL,16,Fthe 82nd Airborne Division.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
