CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774947927
OL,3,CTrump weighs up Kharg Island invasion
OL,4,Cas Israel launches fresh attack on Iran
OL,6,FTrump told the Financial Times on
OL,7,FMonday the US was weighing up an
OL,8,Fattack on Kharg Island, stating that
OL,9,Fhe did not think the area had "any
OL,10,Fdefence".
OL,12,F"We have a lot of options. It would
OL,13,Falso mean we had to be there for a
OL,14,Fwhile," he said.
OL,16,FOn Sunday evening, Trump said it had
OL,17,Fbeen a "big day in Iran" as he praised
OL,18,FUS military efforts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
