OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774947927
OL,3,CTrump weighs up Kharg Island invasion
OL,4,Cas Israel launches fresh attack on Iran
OL,6,F"Many long sought after targets have
OL,7,Fbeen taken out and destroyed by our
OL,8,FGREAT MILITARY, the finest and most
OL,9,Flethal in the World. God bless you
OL,10,Fall!" Trump wrote on Truth Social.
OL,12,FIran's parliament speaker has warned
OL,13,Fthe US against a ground invasion,
OL,14,Fthreatening to set the American troops
OL,15,F"on fire" and step up attacks on the
OL,16,Fnation's allies, according to Iranian
OL,17,Fofficial media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
