OL,3,CTrump weighs up Kharg Island invasion
OL,4,Cas Israel launches fresh attack on Iran
OL,6,F"Our firing continues. Our missiles
OL,7,Fare in place. Our determination and
OL,8,Ffaith have increased," Mohammad Bagher
OL,9,FQalibaf said.
OL,11,FIsrael attacks Iran and Lebanon
OL,13,FIsrael began attacking Iran's
OL,14,Finfrastructure across Tehran early on
OL,15,FMonday morning, the country's military
OL,16,Fsaid in a post on X.
OL,18,FSirens could also be heard near
OL,19,FIsrael's main nuclear research center,
OL,20,Fa part of the country that has been
OL,21,Ftargeted repeatedly over the past days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
