OL,3,CTrump weighs up Kharg Island invasion
OL,4,Cas Israel launches fresh attack on Iran
OL,6,FIsraeli military said its air force
OL,7,Fhad intercepted two drones launched
OL,8,Ffrom Yemen early Monday morning.
OL,10,FThe Iranian-backed Houthi rebels
OL,11,Fclaimed responsibility for launching
OL,12,Ftheir first attack in the current war
OL,13,F- a missile fired at Israel, which was
OL,14,Falso intercepted - on Saturday morning.
OL,16,FIsrael's Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,17,FNetanyahu announced on Sunday he had
OL,18,Ftold his military to widen the
OL,19,Finvasion of southern Lebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
