OL,3,CTrump weighs up Kharg Island invasion
OL,4,Cas Israel launches fresh attack on Iran
OL,6,FNetanyahu claimed military forces had
OL,7,F"eliminated thousands of Hezbollah
OL,8,Fterrorists", as well as "the immense
OL,9,Fthreat of 150,000 missiles and rockets
OL,10,Fthat were intended to destroy the
OL,11,Fcities of Israel".
OL,13,F"I have just instructed to further
OL,14,Fexpand the existing security buffer
OL,15,Fzone. We are determined to
OL,16,Ffundamentally change the situation in
OL,17,Fthe north," Netanyahu said.
OL,19,FStrikes on Gulf nations overnight
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
