OL,3,CTrump weighs up Kharg Island invasion
OL,4,Cas Israel launches fresh attack on Iran
OL,6,FAn Iranian attack on a power and
OL,7,Fdesalination plant in Kuwait has
OL,8,Fkilled an Indian worker, the nation's
OL,9,Fstate-run media said on Monday.
OL,11,FAuthorities said power and water
OL,12,Fsupplies remained constant despite the
OL,13,Fattack.
OL,15,FDesalination plants remain crucial to
OL,16,Fwater supplies in the Gulf Arab
OL,17,Fstates, and Iranian attacks already
OL,18,Fhave damaged some facilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
